#: ../../source/source-citation-specific.rst:252 ../../source/source-citation-specific.rst:252
msgid "When a Staff Researcher accesses a source in order to create a citation, they should record the full, exact date in this attribute. This data is a useful part of quality assurance processes, enabling us to re-visit sources at set points in time to assess whether they have been updated. Recording an access date at the level of the citation also reflects that we may work on some sources for extended periods of time, or work on the same source at different points in time during our research. "
msgstr ""

