#: ../../source/source-citation-specific.rst:322 ../../source/source-citation-specific.rst:322
msgid "Every snapshot made by the Internet Archive contains a timestamp of the time (GMT/UTC) when that snapshot was created. The timestamp is contained in the URL and looks like this: ``20040208204841``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/source-citation-specific.rst:324 ../../source/source-citation-specific.rst:324
msgid "We extract this part of the URL and reformat it to something more human readable (an ISO 8601 format): ``2004-02-08T20:48:41Z``"
msgstr ""

